      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Outstanding mint-condition example that shows exceptionally well throughout. The body, paint, trim, and interior all present at a very high level, with the kind of clean, well-kept appearance buyers hope for but rarely find. It looks like a car that has been carefully maintained and preserved, and it should satisfy a buyer looking for a top-tier example rather than a project or driver-quality car. Expect a car that is ready to enjoy immediately and likely among the nicer examples on the market.",
