      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little vehicle that could make a great budget runabout, project, or spare car. It\u2019s priced with its age and wear in mind, and if you\u2019re handy or just need something inexpensive to work with, there\u2019s real value here. I believe in being straightforward, and this is a chance to pick up a car at a sensible price without any fluff.",
      "price": 7900.0,
